ansible -m ping all
ansible-playbook <playbookname>
ansible vault create <playbookname>
ansible vault edit <playbookname>
defaults, tasks, meta, templates, vars, handlers, files.
By default inventoryfile is hosts, To run your customize inventoryfile
ansible-playbook -i <inventoryfilename> <playbook.yaml>
A single task can notify more than one handler.
ansible <hostname> --become -m yum -a "pkg=httpd state=present"
ansible <hostname> -b -m copy -a "src= /tmp/abc.txt dest= /home
ansible <hostname> -b -m service -a "name=nginx state=started"
ansible <grpname> -b -m user -a "name=ansible password=ansible"
